``````
Yes, unit consumption is counted for Build experiences in AI Hub. The consumption is based on the number of pages and the model used. For example, for documents with 6 to 10 pages, the Default Model charges 5 Units per field, while the Advanced Model charges 20 Units per field. The total cost depends on the number of fields in your schema.
``````
